message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms!

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
